Leading camera phone brand OPPO has announced the launch of a new version of OPPO F3 in the Kenyan market that will be packed with advanced technologies, innovative features and a new sporty vibrant look and design. This is the OPPO F3 FC Barcelona Limited Edition.As a symbol to commemorate the partnership with FC Barcelona and in order to stay true to the colors of the football club, the limited FC Barcelona OPPO F3 will feature an outstanding color with several identical features besides a gold insignia that fans are going to find very appealing.From the announcement made, the OPPO F3 FC Barcelona Limited Edition will feature a red color with the OPPO and Barca logo on the back and a golden accent that reads &ldquo;FC Barcelona Official Partner&rdquo; at the bottom.The red color is apparently interpreted as a reflection of the spirit of the team which is the pride of Barcelona.The OPPO F3 FC Barcelona Limited Edition will be unveiled in the market next week. However, OPPO has neither disclosed the selling price nor the available units but gives a little information that the sale will be only within a limited time frame.Each device will be bundled with a FC Barcelona related special gift pack yet to be disclosed during the official release.On the specifications and features, F3 FC Barcelona Limited Edition will still have the high resolution dual front camera, wide angle group selfie function and high specs.The OPPO F3 FC Barcelona Limited Edition is the device to wait for next week.